<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AirWatch BD | Intelligent Air Quality Monitoring</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: { sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'] },
                    colors: {
                        bgDark: '#0a0a14',
                        panelBg: '#1a1a2e',
                        accentCyan: '#00d4ff',
                        accentGreen: '#00ff88',
                        borderDark: '#333355'
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0a0a14; color: #e0e0e0; }
        .glass-panel { background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid #333355; }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff, #00ff88); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 glass-panel border-b border-borderDark px-6 py-4">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight"><span class="text-accentCyan">🌬️ AirWatch</span> BD</div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-6 text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="#map" class="hover:text-accentCyan transition">Live Map</a>
                <a href="#vulnerability" class="hover:text-accentCyan transition">Vulnerability Model</a>
                <a href="#data" class="hover:text-accentCyan transition">Data Sources</a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/your-username/AirWatch-BD" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded bg-borderDark hover:bg-gray-700 transition text-sm font-semibold">
                ⚙️ GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full glass-panel text-xs text-accentGreen border-accentGreen/30">
            🛰 Google Earth Engine · Sentinel-5P TROPOMI · Health Advisories
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">
            Intelligent Air Quality <br>
            <span class="gradient-text">Monitoring for Bangladesh</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg mb-10">
            High-resolution analysis of 7 major atmospheric pollutants across Dhaka City. Powered by Google Earth Engine, dynamically assessing vulnerability and public health risks from 2020 to 2025.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accentCyan">7</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Pollutants Tracked</div>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accentCyan">5</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Years of Data</div>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accentCyan">8</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Vulnerability Factors</div>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accentCyan">Dhaka</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">FAO GAUL Admin-2</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="map" class="px-6 py-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Interactive Dashboard</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Select a date, explore pollutant layers, and click anywhere on the map to generate a localized health advisory.</p>
        
        <div class="w-full h-[750px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-borderDark shadow-2xl shadow-accentCyan/10">
            <iframe 
                src="https://ee-raunaqpreetom88.projects.earthengine.app/view/air-watch-bd" 
                width="100%" 
                height="100%" 
                frameborder="0" 
                style="border:0;" 
                allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-right">
            <a href="https://ee-raunaqpreetom88.projects.earthengine.app/view/air-watch-bd" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-accentCyan hover:underline">↗ Open App in Full Screen</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="vulnerability" class="px-6 py-16 bg-panelBg/50 border-y border-borderDark">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Vulnerability Assessment Model</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        The AirWatch Vulnerability Layer is a dynamically generated spatial composite. It doesn't just look at pollution; it combines atmospheric data with socio-economic and environmental risk factors to identify areas where the population is most at risk.
                    </p>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-accentGreen">Weighted Composite Variables</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3">
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-borderDark pb-2"><span>NO₂ (Nitrogen Dioxide)</span> <span class="text-accentCyan font-bold">20%</span></li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-borderDark pb-2"><span>Population Density (WorldPop)</span> <span class="text-accentCyan font-bold">20%</span></li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-borderDark pb-2"><span>Land Surface Temp (Heat Island)</span> <span class="text-accentCyan font-bold">15%</span></li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-borderDark pb-2"><span>SO₂, CO, Aerosol (10% each)</span> <span class="text-accentCyan font-bold">30%</span></li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-borderDark pb-2"><span>Green-Space Deficit (Inverse NDVI)</span> <span class="text-accentCyan font-bold">10%</span></li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-borderDark pb-2"><span>CH₄ (Methane)</span> <span class="text-accentCyan font-bold">5%</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl border-t-4 border-t-accentCyan">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">🏥 Health Advisories</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">Clicking the map evaluates the normalized ratio of all pollutants against WHO/Local guidelines to generate automated advisories:</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#00e400]"></span> <span class="text-sm">Good</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffff00]"></span> <span class="text-sm">Moderate</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff7e00]"></span> <span class="text-sm">Unhealthy for Sensitive Groups</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff0000]"></span> <span class="text-sm">Unhealthy</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#7e0023]"></span> <span class="text-sm">Very Unhealthy</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#4c0000]"></span> <span class="text-sm text-red-400 font-bold">Hazardous</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="data" class="px-6 py-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Provenance & Data Sources</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                <thead>
                    <tr class="border-b border-borderDark text-accentCyan">
                        <th class="p-4">Parameter</th>
                        <th class="p-4">Dataset / Satellite</th>
                        <th class="p-4">Provider</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-sm text-gray-300">
                    <tr class="border-b border-borderDark hover:bg-panelBg transition">
                        <td class="p-4 font-semibold">NO₂, SO₂, CO, O₃, HCHO, CH₄, Aerosol</td>
                        <td class="p-4">Sentinel-5P TROPOMI (L3 OFFL)</td>
                        <td class="p-4">Copernicus / ESA</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="border-b border-borderDark hover:bg-panelBg transition">
                        <td class="p-4 font-semibold">Population Density</td>
                        <td class="p-4">WorldPop Global Project (100m)</td>
                        <td class="p-4">WorldPop</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="border-b border-borderDark hover:bg-panelBg transition">
                        <td class="p-4 font-semibold">Land Surface Temperature (LST)</td>
                        <td class="p-4">MOD11A1.061 (Terra Land Surface Temp)</td>
                        <td class="p-4">NASA LP DAAC</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="border-b border-borderDark hover:bg-panelBg transition">
                        <td class="p-4 font-semibold">Vegetation / Green Deficit</td>
                        <td class="p-4">MOD13A2.061 (Terra Vegetation Indices)</td>
                        <td class="p-4">NASA LP DAAC</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="hover:bg-panelBg transition">
                        <td class="p-4 font-semibold">Administrative Boundaries</td>
                        <td class="p-4">FAO GAUL 2015 (Level 2)</td>
                        <td class="p-4">FAO</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-bgDark py-8 border-t border-borderDark text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">© 2026 AirWatch BD. Built with Google Earth Engine.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-2">Developed for environmental monitoring and research purposes.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
